opponent.description: A young woman who was trapped in a undergound ruin of demons many years ago. She befriends every foe she comes across with her quick wit, unshakable determination, and refusal to fight. This includes fish monsters, ghost robots, and sentient vegetables. Despite everything, she's still here.
